[[Image:Kunratický les3.jpg|thumb|Panoramic view from Nový hrad u Kunratic.]]

'''Kunratický les''' is a [[forest]]ed area of three square kilometres in [[Prague]].<ref>[http://envis.praha-mesto.cz/rocenky/Pr_02/B3_04.htm Lesy] {{cs icon}}.</ref> It is located in [[Kunratice (Prague)|Kunratice]] district.  The forest is separated from other forested areas by urban settlements.

''Kunratický les'' is visited by 678,000 people per year who use the forest for recreation, sports activities (running, cycling, etc.) or tourism.

