{{CzechRepublic-stub}}

'''Laulau''' is a settlement in [[Saipan]], in the [[Northern Mariana Islands]]. It is located on the central east coast of the island, close to Laulau Beach, at the northern end of [[Magicienne Bay]]. Though fairly isolated, the beach is a popular attraction. The village is connected by road with [[San Vicente, Saipan|San Vicente]], which lies to the south..

